sentence-with-vars: What number0 classes are offered next semester ?
sql: SELECT DISTINCT COURSEalias0.DEPARTMENT , COURSEalias0.NUMBER FROM COURSE AS COURSEalias0 , COURSE_OFFERING AS COURSE_OFFERINGalias0 , SEMESTER AS SEMESTERalias0 WHERE COURSEalias0.COURSE_ID = COURSE_OFFERINGalias0.COURSE_ID AND COURSEalias0.DEPARTMENT = "EECS" AND COURSEalias0.NUMBER < 400 AND COURSEalias0.NUMBER >= 300 AND SEMESTERalias0.SEMESTER = "FA" AND SEMESTERalias0.SEMESTER_ID = COURSE_OFFERINGalias0.SEMESTER AND SEMESTERalias0.YEAR = 2016 ;
